 <div class="post-1742 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-events" id="post-1742">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 2, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1742">Trash Party Time!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/events-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-938" title="events title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/events-title1.png" alt="" width="211" height="56" /></a></p>
<p>Heeeey, it&#8217;s meee, <strong style="color: #800080;">IzzyRo!</strong> Join me and friends this weekend for our <span style="color: #008000;"><strong>GREEN</strong></span> event! I&#8217;ll be there!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/TrashCleanupEvent.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1743" title="TrashCleanupEvent" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/TrashCleanupEvent.jpg" alt="" width="981" height="526" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1742#comments" title="Comment on Trash Party Time!">8 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1720 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart" id="post-1720">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 30, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1720">ekoLogo Art!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Look at this awesome logo that <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>Avi (PonPon447)</strong></span> made for the ekoloko Rangers Forum!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/EkolokoForum-AviPonPon447.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1721" title="EkolokoForum-AviPonPon447" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/EkolokoForum-AviPonPon447.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="369" /></a></p>
<p>Wow&#8230;just WOW! I thought it was so awesome that I just HAD to post it on the blog. WoOoP! Great work, <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>Avi</strong></span>!!!</p>
<p><span style="color: #008000;">Who can name every eko in this picture?</span></p>
<p>If anyone else would like to share a logo or any kind of artwork on the blog &#8212; send to <strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</span>!!!</strong></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1720#comments" title="Comment on ekoLogo Art!">6 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1711 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart category-uncategorized" id="post-1711">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 30, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1711">Super Cuuuute!!!!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p>Check out this helpful and fun comic created by <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>cutepie123</strong></span>!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/how-to-do-faces-in-ekoloko-Cutepie123.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1712" title="how to do faces in ekoloko-Cutepie123" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/how-to-do-faces-in-ekoloko-Cutepie123.png" alt="" width="635" height="407" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Thanks, cutepie123!!! I can&#8217;t wait to see more of your art. Send to <strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</span>!!!</strong></span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1711#comments" title="Comment on Super Cuuuute!!!!">2 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1704 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-1704">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 30, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1704">1stLady&#8217;s Very Last Blog Post</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p>We&#8217;ve said our goodbyes and yet I found I still had some time and I wanted to share something with all of you.<a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/1stLady_101612.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-863" title="1stLady_101612" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/1stLady_101612.png" alt="" width="156" height="323" /></a></p>
<p>ekoloko is truly a special place &#8211; where long-lasting friendships are quickly found. I know I made quite a few new friends here! Remember that <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>THIS</strong></span> is the true reason for playing on ekoloko &#8212; and never forget the people you met or the friends you made.</p>
<p>And as for IzzyRo &#8211; I <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>KNOW</strong></span> she will take good care of you all &#8211; so please take good care of her! She loves you just as much as I do, and she <strong><span style="color: #800080;">ALWAYS</span></strong> has <strong><span style="color: #800080;">YOUR</span></strong> best interests at heart!</p>
<p>Always make me proud! See you soon!</p>
<p>HUGS!</p>
<p>1stLady</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1704#comments" title="Comment on 1stLady&#8217;s Very Last Blog Post">4 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1686 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-rangers" id="post-1686">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 30, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1686">New Rangers!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>I am happy to announce our newest group of Advanced Rangers: <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>avi333, disniyxdca, GreenUnicorn, hibou123, moneypenny1, and rehab2!!!</strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/RangerGroup4-29-13.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1687" title="RangerGroup4-29-13" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/RangerGroup4-29-13.jpg" alt="" width="819" height="242" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">The Rangers who missed the previous ceremony are also invited: <strong>JinJer, Randysavage, and dad321!!!</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px; color: #008000;">All Advanced Rangers are invited to the ceremony!</span></p>
<p><strong style="font-size: 13px;">WHEN</strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">: Sunday, May 5th at 2pm EDT, 21:00 Israel, 20:00 France</span></p>
<p><strong>WHERE</strong>: The best world EVER: ekoloko&#8230;any room&#8230;you&#8217;ll see a message <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif' alt=':-P' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">If you can&#8217;t come to this ceremony please email <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>support_us@ekoloko.com </strong><span style="color: #000000;">and we can work out something for you. <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif' alt=':-D' class='wp-smiley' /> </span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">Congrats new Rangers!!!</span></strong></span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1686#comments" title="Comment on New Rangers!">3 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1627 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-donuts category-ekoart category-uncategorized" id="post-1627">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 28, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1627">Art from the Heart</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Here are a few works of art for 1stLady and Megara&#8230;</p>
<p><span style="color: #333399;"><strong><em>Created by Donuts:</em></strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Donuts1stLadyMegara.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1651" title="Donuts1stLadyMegara" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Donuts1stLadyMegara.png" alt="" width="649" height="800" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #333399;"><strong><em>Created by mazaii and avrila:</em></strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/mazaiiAvrila1stLadyMegara.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1652" title="mazaiiAvrila1stLadyMegara" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/mazaiiAvrila1stLadyMegara.jpg" alt="" width="817" height="491" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Amazing!</span></p>
<p>Thank you so much for creating such heartfelt and beautiful works of art. I know 1stLady and Megara will be warmed and comforted by them.</p>
<p>Want to see <span style="color: #800080;">YOUR</span> art on the blog? Send to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-746" title="donuts corner" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" alt="" width="327" height="67" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Look at these touching comics created by May (Donuts)&#8230;</span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Comics-Diane.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1628" title="Comics-Diane" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Comics-Diane.png" alt="" width="649" height="800" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Comics-Hannah.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1629" title="Comics-Hannah" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Comics-Hannah.png" alt="" width="723" height="700" /></a></p>
<p>And a message:</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;"><em>&#8220;Hannah and Diane. I can&#8217;t believe that I&#8217;m writing it now&#8230; You are amazing managers. I love you so much, and I&#8217;m sure all ekoloko love you, too.</em></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;"><em>I hope you&#8217;ll come to visit us &#8211; we are waiting. </em></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;"><em>Good luck in everything you will do <span style="color: #ff0000;">♥</span></em></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;"><em>The Ekos&#8221;</em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Thank you to May and all of the ekos involved! Your compassion means so much to us!!!</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=14" title="View all posts in Donuts" rel="category">Donuts</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1627#comments" title="Comment on Art from the Heart">9 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1615 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-1615">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 28, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1615">Success!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/ekoHappy.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1616 alignleft" title="ekoHappy" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/ekoHappy.png" alt="" width="86" height="86" /></a><img class="size-full wp-image-1617 alignleft" style="font-size: 13px;" title="ekoThumbsup" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/ekoThumbsup.png" alt="" width="73" height="81" /><span style="font-size: 13px;">You may now send blog related requests to <span style="color: #008000;"><strong>THE BLOG</strong></span> at </span><span style="font-size: 13px;">usa_blog@ekoloko.com! </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">All other requests should be sent to support_us@ekoloko.com or by using the Question Mark in ekoloko.</span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1615#respond" title="Comment on Success!">No Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1588 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews" id="post-1588">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 27, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1588">Oops!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a style="font-size: 13px;" href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/embarrassedface.jpg" ><img class="alignleft  wp-image-1589" title="Embarrassed Face" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/embarrassedface.jpg" alt="" width="127" height="112" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Hello all you loving, caring, patient, and understanding ekos!  ;-)</span></p>
<p>We are having technical difficulties with the blog email address so <span style="color: #008000;">for now</span> please email your requests to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="mailto:support_us@ekoloko.com" target="_blank">support_us@ekoloko.com</a><span style="color: #000000;"> or by using the Question Mark in ekoloko.  Thank yoooouuuu! <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/QuestionMark.jpg" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1598" title="QuestionMark" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/QuestionMark.jpg" alt="" width="65" height="61" /></a></span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"><br />
</span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1588#comments" title="Comment on Oops!">1 Comment &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1548 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-uncategorized" id="post-1548">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 24, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1548">Check Me Out!  Posting Like a Pro!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a style="font-size: 13px;" href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/AMessageFromIzzyRo1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1571" title="AMessageFromIzzyRo" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/AMessageFromIzzyRo1.png" alt="" width="355" height="79" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/izzyroAvatar3.png" ><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1562" title="izzyroAvatar3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/izzyroAvatar3.png" alt="" width="113" height="215" /></a><span style="color: #000000;">Oooooh, myyyy&#8230; So it has come to this&#8230; </span></span><span style="color: #000000;">IzzyRo<span style="font-size: 13px;"> posting? On the </span>BLOG<span style="font-size: 13px;">?</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">OY!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">But seriously&#8230;it&#8217;s going to be fun! I will keep you up to date on all the special events, new rangers, Eko art, jokes, probably lots of pictures of my crazy kitty, and more!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">I&#8217;ll be seeing ya. <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">~IzzyRo~</span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1548#comments" title="Comment on Check Me Out!  Posting Like a Pro!">7 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1531 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-rangers" id="post-1531">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on April 23, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1531">Sharing Secrets</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>And so she said &#8211; she has a secret. A secret? Yes &#8211; and what is this special secret? Well, I told you that I&#8217;d never be far, and that I&#8217;d always have a way of knowing what you were doing, and how everyone was. Am I omniscient? Am I a GOD? No&#8230;..</p>
<p>So, as promised &#8211; here it is &#8211; the <span style="color: #3366ff;"><strong>SECRET</strong></span> &#8211; but wait! Do I reveal it to you now? Or do I wait and make you squirm?</p>
<p>OK OK, I&#8217;ll tell! Can you see the resemblance?</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/1stLady41813.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1481" title="1stLady41813" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/1stLady41813.png" alt="" width="146" height="260" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/izzyro.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1537" title="izzyro" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/izzyro.png" alt="" width="149" height="233" /></a></p>
<p>Alright, alright &#8211; so we don&#8217;t look alike! (We do have the same taste in shoes!!!!!)</p>
<p>But we ARE related! IzzyRo is my niece Rose &#8211; her mother is my sister &#8211; and she lives in New York and I see her every time I travel to NY to visit my family! When I first looked for managers to work for ekoloko I thought of Rose and I was right &#8211; she was a great choice then, and she is a great choice now for continuing to manage the community and keep you all busy and having fun! So remember &#8211; I will ALWAYS be with you &#8211; thru Rose, and in my heart!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>We had a really emotional ranger ceremony this past week as we cheered on our newest Advanced Rangers and watched them get their halos!</p>
<p>Congratulations again to: MasterShef1, PeterLanzani and Maor82!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/rangersRkewlCeremony42113.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1532" title="rangersRkewlCeremony42113" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/rangersRkewlCeremony42113.png" alt="" width="704" height="381" /></a></p>
<p>Oh and how could we forget JOY?! Late last week IzzyRo and Jump4Joy19 met up for a mini Ranger ceremony that was no less exciting!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/RangerJoy.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1533" title="RangerJoy" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/RangerJoy.jpg" alt="" width="323" height="223" /></a></p>
<p>We are so happy to have all our new Advanced Rangers &#8211; remember to continue setting an example and making us proud!</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Practical Stuff:</span> You should all have a new button that allows you to send messages to the world about good behavior. Please do NOT abuse this feature. You should now also have the Hangman game as part of your Rangers with Class game! Invite Ekos who are Level 8 or lower and help them learn about ekoloko through this fun game! Keep up the good work!</p>
<p>Next week IzzyRo will select the next group of Rangers of the Week &#8211; so look for her blog posts and get busy helping and being friendly and doing what you need to do! Good luck to all my Ekos out there!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/events-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-22" title="events title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/events-title1.png" alt="" width="222" height="81" /></a></p>
<p>This coming weekend we will have some puddle fun as we splash around in the rain and look for the flowers! So get your rain gear on as we say goodbye to April and turn our faces to the sun!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/loader.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1545" title="loader" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/loader.png" alt="" width="912" height="508" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1531#comments" title="Comment on Sharing Secrets">5 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 
